OL,3,CIndian takeway prosecuted following
OL,4,C'serious' food hygiene violations
OL,6,FAn Indian restaurant in Sheerness has
OL,7,Fbeen fined more than #15,000 after it
OL,8,Fwas found to pose a significant risk
OL,9,Fto public health.
OL,11,FSwale Borough Council investigated
OL,12,FMasala Reef, on Hope Street,
OL,13,Fthroughout 2024 and 2025.
OL,15,FOfficers found serious violations of
OL,16,Fthe food hygiene and safety provision
OL,17,Fon several visits, including an
OL,18,Finfestation of mice, poor standards of
OL,19,Fcleaning, and processes and equipment
OL,20,Fwhich could lead to contamination.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
