FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1778505068
OL,3,CIndian takeway prosecuted following
OL,4,C'serious' food hygiene violations
OL,6,FThe council tried to provide advice
OL,7,Fand intervene, but the restaurant did
OL,8,Fnot fix the issues. It eventually
OL,9,Fobtained a court order to close the
OL,10,Ftakeaway, and later prosecuted it.
OL,12,FFollowing on from the councils action,
OL,13,Fthe owners of the restaurant have been
OL,14,Fworking closely with environmental
OL,15,Fhealth officers. It has since reopened.
OL,17,FSwale Borough Council says they are
OL,18,Fnow compliant with legal requirements,
OL,19,Fand at their last food hygiene
OL,20,Finspection, rated Masala Reef as four
OL,21,Fout of five.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
