PN,41203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1778505068
OL,3,CIndian takeway prosecuted following
OL,4,C'serious' food hygiene violations
OL,6,FIn a statement, the council said:
OL,7,F"Serious breaches of food hygiene and
OL,8,Fsafety processes have cost a Sheerness
OL,9,Ftakeaway more than #15,000.
OL,11,F"Our officers visited Masala Reef, an
OL,12,FIndian takeaway on Hope Street,
OL,13,Fmultiple times throughout 2024 and
OL,14,F2025 to inspect the restaurant and
OL,15,Ffound serious violations of the food
OL,16,Fhygiene and safety provision.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/5
