PN,41204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1778505068
OL,3,CIndian takeway prosecuted following
OL,4,C'serious' food hygiene violations
OL,6,F"This included an infestation of mice,
OL,7,Fpoor standards of cleaning, and
OL,8,Fprocesses and equipment which could
OL,9,Flead to contamination, posing a
OL,10,Fsignificant risk to public health.
OL,12,F"The restaurant did not fix these
OL,13,Fserious issues despite our
OL,14,Finterventions and advice, including
OL,15,Fobtaining a court order to temporarily
OL,16,Fclose the business, ultimately
OL,17,Fresulting in the prosecution.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/5
