PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1778505068
OL,3,CIndian takeway prosecuted following
OL,4,C'serious' food hygiene violations
OL,6,F"The owners have since worked closely
OL,7,Fwith us and are now complying with
OL,8,Ftheir legal requirements and, at their
OL,9,Flast food hygiene inspection, the
OL,10,Frestaurant has been issued a food
OL,11,Fhygiene rating of 4, good."
